tm_medium=ios&amp;triedRedirect=true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Baseball’s Hall of Fame doesn’t care about player salaries</a> </strong>and <strong><a href=\"https://almostcooperstown.substack.com/p/comparing-all-star-centerfielders?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=1216321&amp;post_id=197680351&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=false&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Comparing All-Star centerfielders Brett Butler &amp; Steve Finley</a> </strong>by  </p></li>\n<li><p>⚾ <strong><a href=\"https://baseballprojection.substack.com/p/how-far-did-pujols-fall?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=5914842&amp;post_id=197109768&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">How far did Pujols fall?</a> </strong>and <strong><a href=\"https://baseballprojection.substack.com/p/how-close-did-mantle-come-to-his?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=5914842&amp;post_id=197735970&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">How close did Mantle come to his potential?</a> </strong>by  </p></li>\n<li><p>⚾ <strong><a href=\"https://themetropolitan.substack.com/p/the-baby-mets?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=174126&amp;post_id=197668877&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Baby Mets</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏒 <strong><a href=\"https://gabarr.substack.com/p/who-are-the-nhls-underrated-goalies?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=2577590&amp;post_id=196944314&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_bla